trans-unit.source: Results returned after a call to <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges*> when enumerating operation responses returned by the <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Resultater returnert etter kall til <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges*>under opplisting av operasjonen svar ble returnert av den <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse"> </xref> klasse.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges*>

trans-unit.source: ChangeOperationResponse objects are not intended to be constructed directly by a user of this library.
trans-unit.target: ChangeOperationResponse objekter er ikke ment å konstrueres direkte fra en bruker av dette biblioteket.

trans-unit.source: Instead, references are returned when enumerating the operation responses returned via the enumerator on the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> class.
trans-unit.target: Returnert i stedet referanser er under opplisting av operasjonen svar returnerte via enumeratoren på <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>klasse.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> submits pending changes to the data service collected by the <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext> since the last call to <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>sender ventende endringer til datatjenesten samles inn av den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext>siden forrige kall til <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext></xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: Changes are added to the context by calling <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddObject%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddLink%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteObject%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteLink%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.Detach%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DetachLink%2A>, and similar methods.
trans-unit.target: Endringene er lagt til i konteksten ved å kalle <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddObject%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddLink%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteObject%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteLink%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.Detach%2A>, <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DetachLink%2A>, og lignende metoder.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DetachLink%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.Detach%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteLink%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.DeleteObject%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddLink%2A> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.AddObject%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A> returns a <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> that represents the response to all operations sent to the data service.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>Returnerer en <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>som representerer svar til alle operasjoner som er sendt til vertstjenesten.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse></xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceContext.SaveChanges%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse> object includes a sequence of ChangeOperationResponse objects that, in turn, contain a sequence of <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor> or <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor> instances that represent the changes that were persisted or attempted.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>objektet inneholder en sekvens med ChangeOperationResponse-objekter som i sin tur inneholde en sekvens med <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor>eller <xref:System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor>forekomster som representerer endringer som ble fast eller forsøkt.</xref:System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor> </xref:System.Data.Services.Client.DataServiceResponse>

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor"></xref> or <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor"></xref> modified by a change operation.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor"> </xref> endret av en endring-operasjon.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor"></xref> or <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor"></xref> modified by a change operation.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.EntityDescriptor"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Data.Services.Client.LinkDescriptor"> </xref> endret av en endring-operasjon.
